e appropriate to monitor patient response as well as serum potassium level, blood pressure and heart rate during coadministration, especially if the beta-2 agonist is administered systemically or by nebulizer.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/163919/', '', 'Mometasone furoate, Umeclidinium, Aclidinium, Glycopyrronium, Mometasone, Cromoglicic acid, Ipratropium, Epinephrine, Beclomethasone dipropionate', 'Omalizumab, Tezepelumab, Mercaptopurine, Benralizumab, Caffeine, Reslizumab, Mepolizumab, Roflumilast, Bromotheophylline', 1767369485);
